==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underplot
<hw>Un"der*plot`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
series of events in a play, proceeding collaterally with the main story,
and subservient to it.</def> <rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A clandestine scheme; a trick.</def>
<rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underpoise</ent>⟦br⟧
